### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَيَعْبُدُونَ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ مَا لَا يَنفَعُهُمْ وَلَا يَضُرُّهُمْ ۗ وَكَانَ ٱلْكَافِرُ عَلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ ظَهِيرًا</span>

### English

Yet they worship besides Allah what can neither benefit nor harm them. And the disbeliever always collaborates against their Lord.